<div id="review_2533413597" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2533413597" />
    <a title="Dawn C" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/14948447-dawn-c"><img alt="Dawn C" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1535435406p2/14948447.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2533413597?book_show_action=true">Dec 13, 2018</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Dawn C" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Dawn C" href="/user/show/14948447-dawn-c">Dawn C</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/14948447-dawn-c?shelf=group-shelf">group-shelf</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/14948447-dawn-c?shelf=media-ibooks">media-ibooks</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/14948447-dawn-c?shelf=loved">loved</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/14948447-dawn-c?shelf=5th-read-all-the-books-challenge">5th-read-all-the-books-challenge</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2533413597" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer71010664105741938">I didn’t know what to expect but I was blown completely leftfield. Set in the 22nd century where Communist China now sets the political and social agenda, we follow the slightly unsympathetic titular character Zhang Zhong Shan through a series of interconnected events involving him and the people whose lives he somehow touches. This is a science fiction story that avoids all the usual tropes and instead gives the reader a microcosm of a personal journey. The writing is minimalistic and our view </span>
  <span id="freeText71010664105741938" style="display:none">I didn’t know what to expect but I was blown completely leftfield. Set in the 22nd century where Communist China now sets the political and social agenda, we follow the slightly unsympathetic titular character Zhang Zhong Shan through a series of interconnected events involving him and the people whose lives he somehow touches. This is a science fiction story that avoids all the usual tropes and instead gives the reader a microcosm of a personal journey. The writing is minimalistic and our view through Zhang as he works a boring construction tech job and has unsatisfying relationships with men is deliberately narrow. But even the most stubbornly passive can’t maintain status quo forever.</span>
  <a data-text-id="71010664105741938" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


